nd dealers and impact of nonrecurring tax items adjusted ebitda is calculated by excluding depreciation amortization and other net income or expense from adjusted operating earnings organic sales represents the change in net sales excluding currency translation effects and the impact of acquisitions we present the adjusted financial measures because we consider them to be important supplemental measures of our performance and believe them to be useful in analyzing ongoing results from operations the adjusted financial measures are not measurements of our financial performance under gaap and should not be considered an alternative to gross margin operating expenses operating earnings loss and earnings loss per share  diluted under gaap the adjusted financial measures have limitations as analytical tools and should not be considered in isolation or as a substitute for analysis of our results as reported under gaap our presentation of the adjusted financial measures should not be construed as an indication that our future results will be unaffected by unusual or infrequent items we compensate for these limitations by providing prominence of our gaap results and using the adjusted financial measures only as a supplement the following table reconciles net sales to organic net sales for the years and reportable operating segments indicated    jul   c  cybernet data systems inc all rights reserved more from marketwatch more coverage john mccain gives trump a win then gives senate an earful amd earnings give investors what they wanted now it must deliver here’s why oil just scored its biggest oneday rally of  most popular here’s why oil just scored its biggest oneday rally of  amd earnings give investors what they wanted now it must deliver the highest paid athletes in the world in one chart elon musk just burned mark zuckerberg in a tweet about ai scaramucci says he regrets calling trump a hack marketwatch partner center we want to hear from you join the conversation comme